{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 115 "For demonstration purposes it is very ha
ndy to be able to construct polynomials with predetermined roots.  Use
 the " }{TEXT 258 6 "expand" }{TEXT -1 58 " command to construct a pol
ynomial with roots   -2, 5, 5, " }{XPPEDIT 18 0 "-1/2" "6#,$*&\"\"\"F%
